      <section class="module tab-markets-regional">
       <header class="module-header">
        <h4 class="module-heading">
         Regional Markets
         <span class="title-last">
          News
         </span>
        </h4>
       </header>
       <section class="module-content">
        <!-- TABS -->
        <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tab-table" id="regionMarketsTabs" width="100%">
         <tbody>
          <tr>
           <th class="tab-1 tab-button current" data-target="tab-markets-us" width="33.333333333333336%">
            United States
           </th>
           <th class="tab-2 tab-button" data-target="tab-markets-emea" width="33.333333333333336%">
            Europe &amp; Middle East
           </th>
           <th class="tab-3 tab-button" data-target="tab-markets-asia" width="33.333333333333336%">
            Asia Pacific
           </th>
          </tr>
         </tbody>
        </table>
        <style>
         .tab-markets-regional .tabs {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li span,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li span.hrefClone{
    background: none !important;
    border: none !important;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current{
    background: #f5f5f5 !important;
    padding-bottom: 0px !important;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current span{
    padding-bottom: 13px;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current span,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current span.hrefClone{
    font-family: knowledge-medium,helvetica,arial,sans-serif;
}
#tab-markets-us .news-headline-list,
#tab-markets-emea .news-headline-list,
#tab-markets-asia .news-headline-list{
    margin-bottom: 40px;
}
        </style>
       </section>
      </section>
      <script>
       $(function(){

    var tabs       = $('#regionMarketsTabs .tab-button');
    var tabTargets = []

    function compileTabTargets(tabs, targetsArray) {
      for (i=0; i < tabs.length; i++) {
        var tabTargetId = $(tabs[i]).data('target');
        var tabTarget   = $('#'+tabTargetId);
        targetsArray.push(tabTarget);
      }
    }

    function tabClick(tabs, targets) {
      tabs.on('click', function() {
        var targetId = $(this).data('target');
        var target   = $('#'+targetId);

        // SHOW / HIDE MODULES
        for (j=0; j < targets.length; j++) {
          var module = targets[j][0];

          if (targetId != module.id) {
            $(module).addClass('hidden');
          } else {
            $(module).removeClass('hidden');
          }
        }

        // ADD CURRENT CLASS TO TAB
        for (k=0; k < tabs.length; k++) {
          if (tabs[k] == this) {
            $(tabs[k]).addClass('current');
          } else {
            $(tabs[k]).removeClass('current');
          }
        }
      });
    }

    // LAZY LOAD IMAGES
    function lazyLoadImages(images) {
      for(l=0; images.length > l; l++){
          var image = images[l];
          if (typeof image.dataset.lazySrc != "undefined") {
            if (image.src != image.dataset.lazySrc) {
              image.src = image.dataset.lazySrc;
            }
          }
        }
    }

    function lazyLoadEvent() {
      if ("" == "1") {
        var tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-button');
        if (tabs.length > 0) {
          for(i=0; tabs.length > i; i++){
            if (i == 0) {
              var targetIdOne     = tabs[i].dataset.target,
                  tabTargetOne       = document.getElementById(targetIdOne),
                  tabTargetOneImages = tabTargetOne.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetOneImages);
            }

            tabs[i].addEventListener('click', function() {
              var tabTargetId     = this.dataset.target,
                  tabTarget       = document.getElementById(tabTargetId),
                  tabTargetImages = tabTarget.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetImages);
            });
          }
        }
      }
    }

    compileTabTargets(tabs, tabTargets);
    tabClick(tabs, tabTargets);
    lazyLoadEvent();
    
  });
      </script>

      <div class="section markets-module mod-tabs-table">
       <div class="sectionContent">
        <div id="ad-div-mpu">
         <div class="section markets-module">
          <div class="sectionContent">
           <link href="//s2.reutersmedia.net/resources_v2/css/core-markets.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
           <style>
            #marketslogo-bottom iframe{height:50px;}
           </style>
           <div class="linebreak">
           </div>
           <header class="module-header">
            <h4 class="module-heading">
             <a href="/finance/markets">
              <span class="title-last">
               Markets
              </span>
             </a>
             <div class="marketslogo" id="marketslogo">
             </div>
            </h4>
           </header>
           <div class="linebreak">
           </div>
           <section class="module module-no-margin">
            <section class="module-content">
             <!-- TABS -->
             <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tab-table blend small" id="marketsModuleTabs" width="100%">
              <tbody>
               <tr>
                <th class="tab-1 tab-button current" data-target="leadstocks" width="25.0%">
                 STOCKS
                </th>
                <th class="tab-2 tab-button" data-target="leadbonds" width="25.0%">
                 BONDS
                </th>
                <th class="tab-3 tab-button" data-target="leadcurrencies" width="25.0%">
                 CURRENCIES
                </th>
                <th class="tab-4 tab-button" data-target="leadcommodities" width="25.0%">
                 COMMODITIES
                </th>
               </tr>
              </tbody>
             </table>
            </section>
           </section>
           <script>
            $(function(){

    var tabs       = $('#marketsModuleTabs .tab-button');
    var tabTargets = []

    function compileTabTargets(tabs, targetsArray) {
      for (i=0; i < tabs.length; i++) {
        var tabTargetId = $(tabs[i]).data('target');
        var tabTarget   = $('#'+tabTargetId);
        targetsArray.push(tabTarget);
      }
    }

    function tabClick(tabs, targets) {
      tabs.on('click', function() {
        var targetId = $(this).data('target');
        var target   = $('#'+targetId);

        // SHOW / HIDE MODULES
        for (j=0; j < targets.length; j++) {
          var module = targets[j][0];

          if (targetId != module.id) {
            $(module).addClass('hidden');
          } else {
            $(module).removeClass('hidden');
          }
        }

        // ADD CURRENT CLASS TO TAB
        for (k=0; k < tabs.length; k++) {
          if (tabs[k] == this) {
            $(tabs[k]).addClass('current');
          } else {
            $(tabs[k]).removeClass('current');
          }
        }
      });
    }

    // LAZY LOAD IMAGES
    function lazyLoadImages(images) {
      for(l=0; images.length > l; l++){
          var image = images[l];
          if (typeof image.dataset.lazySrc != "undefined") {
            if (image.src != image.dataset.lazySrc) {
              image.src = image.dataset.lazySrc;
            }
          }
        }
    }

    function lazyLoadEvent() {
      if ("" == "1") {
        var tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-button');
        if (tabs.length > 0) {
          for(i=0; tabs.length > i; i++){
            if (i == 0) {
              var targetIdOne     = tabs[i].dataset.target,
                  tabTargetOne       = document.getElementById(targetIdOne),
                  tabTargetOneImages = tabTargetOne.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetOneImages);
            }

            tabs[i].addEventListener('click', function() {
              var tabTargetId     = this.dataset.target,
                  tabTarget       = document.getElementById(tabTargetId),
                  tabTargetImages = tabTarget.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetImages);
            });
          }
        }
      }
    }

    compileTabTargets(tabs, tabTargets);
    tabClick(tabs, tabTargets);
    lazyLoadEvent();
    
  });
           </script>
           <div id="leadstocks">

             .index-data-list .index-chart { display: none; }
            </style>

                     S&amp;P »

                       3,140.52

            <script src="https://content.markitcdn.com/www.chartworks.io/content/chartworks/dist/1.4.8/js/chartworks.min.js" type="text/javascript">
            </script>
            <script>
             $('.index-name').bind('click', function() {
        var index       = $(this),
            indexRic    = index.attr('data-ric'),
            indices     = $('.index-data-container').find('.index-name'),
            indexTab    = index.find('.index-tab');

        for (i=0;indices.length > i;i++) {
            $(indices[i]).removeClass('active');
            $('.index-tab').removeClass('active');
        }
        index.addClass('active');
        indexTab.addClass('active');
        renderChart(window.chartworks_token, indexRic)
    });

    const first_ric = $('.index-name')[0].dataset.ric;

    function getChartData(obj) {
        window.chartworks_token = obj.access_token;
        renderChart(obj.access_token, first_ric);
    }

    
    function renderChart(token, ric) {

        // Set the chart inputs
        var chartInputs = {
          "symbol": ric,
          "realTime": false,
          "cultureCode": "en-US",
          "fontColor": "#999999",
          "fontSize": 18,
          "upperPanelHeight": 144,
          "lowerPanelHeight": 0,
          "numDays": 1,
          "priceLineColor": "#ff8000",
          "priceLineWidth": 3,
          "showVolume": false,
          "volumeColor": "#ff8000",
          "width": 556,
          "xGridLineColor": "#ffffff",
          "xGridLineWidth": 1,
          "yGridLineColor": "#dddddd",
          "yGridLineWidth": 1
        };

        // Stringify & Encode Inputs
        var encoded = encodeURIComponent(JSON.stringify(chartInputs, null));

        // Create API call
        var url = "https://api.markitondemand.com/apiman-gateway/MOD/chartworks-image/1/Chart/price?inputs=" + encoded + "&access_token=" + token;

        // Append to our target
        $(".index-data-container .index-chart img").remove();
        $('<img />').attr("src", url).appendTo(".index-data-container .index-chart");


    }
            </script>
            <script src="https://apiservice.reuters.com/api/service/modtoken?method=get&amp;format=json&amp;callback=getChartData&amp;apikey=72461C50B1CEAD3135BA6BDA53B203D3&amp;deviceid=E7CDD293-9C3A-5AB9-9181-58E1B572DD44" type="text/javascript">
            </script>

     <script>
      const footer_product_links = document.querySelectorAll('footer .product-container a');

if (typeof(analytics) != 'undefinded') {
	for (i=0; footer_product_links.length > i; i++) {
		footer_product_links[i].addEventListener('mousedown', function() {
			let url = this.href;
			let name = this.getElementsByClassName('prod-title')[0].innerText.toLowerCase();
			analytics.track('click link', {
				type: 'event',
				label: this.href,
				category: 'footer '+name
			})
		});
	}
}
     </script>

      <section class="module tab-markets-regional">
       <header class="module-header">
        <h4 class="module-heading">
         Regional Markets
         <span class="title-last">
          News
         </span>
        </h4>
       </header>
       <section class="module-content">
        <!-- TABS -->
        <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tab-table" id="regionMarketsTabs" width="100%">
         <tbody>
          <tr>
           <th class="tab-1 tab-button current" data-target="tab-markets-us" width="33.333333333333336%">
            United States
           </th>
           <th class="tab-2 tab-button" data-target="tab-markets-emea" width="33.333333333333336%">
            Europe &amp; Middle East
           </th>
           <th class="tab-3 tab-button" data-target="tab-markets-asia" width="33.333333333333336%">
            Asia Pacific
           </th>
          </tr>
         </tbody>
        </table>
        <style>
         .tab-markets-regional .tabs {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li span,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li span.hrefClone{
    background: none !important;
    border: none !important;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current{
    background: #f5f5f5 !important;
    padding-bottom: 0px !important;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current span{
    padding-bottom: 13px;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current span,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current span.hrefClone{
    font-family: knowledge-medium,helvetica,arial,sans-serif;
}
#tab-markets-us .news-headline-list,
#tab-markets-emea .news-headline-list,
#tab-markets-asia .news-headline-list{
    margin-bottom: 40px;
}
        </style>
       </section>
      </section>
      <script>
       $(function(){

    var tabs       = $('#regionMarketsTabs .tab-button');
    var tabTargets = []

    function compileTabTargets(tabs, targetsArray) {
      for (i=0; i < tabs.length; i++) {
        var tabTargetId = $(tabs[i]).data('target');
        var tabTarget   = $('#'+tabTargetId);
        targetsArray.push(tabTarget);
      }
    }

    function tabClick(tabs, targets) {
      tabs.on('click', function() {
        var targetId = $(this).data('target');
        var target   = $('#'+targetId);

        // SHOW / HIDE MODULES
        for (j=0; j < targets.length; j++) {
          var module = targets[j][0];

          if (targetId != module.id) {
            $(module).addClass('hidden');
          } else {
            $(module).removeClass('hidden');
          }
        }

        // ADD CURRENT CLASS TO TAB
        for (k=0; k < tabs.length; k++) {
          if (tabs[k] == this) {
            $(tabs[k]).addClass('current');
          } else {
            $(tabs[k]).removeClass('current');
          }
        }
      });
    }

    // LAZY LOAD IMAGES
    function lazyLoadImages(images) {
      for(l=0; images.length > l; l++){
          var image = images[l];
          if (typeof image.dataset.lazySrc != "undefined") {
            if (image.src != image.dataset.lazySrc) {
              image.src = image.dataset.lazySrc;
            }
          }
        }
    }

    function lazyLoadEvent() {
      if ("" == "1") {
        var tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-button');
        if (tabs.length > 0) {
          for(i=0; tabs.length > i; i++){
            if (i == 0) {
              var targetIdOne     = tabs[i].dataset.target,
                  tabTargetOne       = document.getElementById(targetIdOne),
                  tabTargetOneImages = tabTargetOne.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetOneImages);
            }

            tabs[i].addEventListener('click', function() {
              var tabTargetId     = this.dataset.target,
                  tabTarget       = document.getElementById(tabTargetId),
                  tabTargetImages = tabTarget.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetImages);
            });
          }
        }
      }
    }

    compileTabTargets(tabs, tabTargets);
    tabClick(tabs, tabTargets);
    lazyLoadEvent();
    
  });
      </script>
      <section class="module" id="tab-markets-us">
       <section class="module-content">
        <div class="news-headline-list medium">
         <article class="story">
          <div class="story-content">
           <a href="/article/canada-natio-rail-labor/update-7-canadas-biggest-rail-strike-in-a-decade-ends-backlogs-could-nag-shippers-idUSL1N2860EO">
            <h3 class="story-title">
             UPDATE 7-Canada's biggest rail strike in a decade ends, backlogs could nag shippers
            </h3>
           </a>
           <div class="contributor">
           </div>
           <p>
            Canada's longest
railroad strike in a decade ended on Tuesday as Canadian
National Railway Co reached a tentative agreement with
workers, but shippers warned it could take weeks before service
bounces back to normal.
           </p>
           <time class="article-time">
            <span class="timestamp">
             5:02pm EST

           <script>
            $(function(){

    var tabs       = $('#marketsModuleTabs .tab-button');
    var tabTargets = []

    function compileTabTargets(tabs, targetsArray) {
      for (i=0; i < tabs.length; i++) {
        var tabTargetId = $(tabs[i]).data('target');
        var tabTarget   = $('#'+tabTargetId);
        targetsArray.push(tabTarget);
      }
    }

    function tabClick(tabs, targets) {
      tabs.on('click', function() {
        var targetId = $(this).data('target');
        var target   = $('#'+targetId);

        // SHOW / HIDE MODULES
        for (j=0; j < targets.length; j++) {
          var module = targets[j][0];

          if (targetId != module.id) {
            $(module).addClass('hidden');
          } else {
            $(module).removeClass('hidden');
          }
        }

        // ADD CURRENT CLASS TO TAB
        for (k=0; k < tabs.length; k++) {
          if (tabs[k] == this) {
            $(tabs[k]).addClass('current');
          } else {
            $(tabs[k]).removeClass('current');
          }
        }
      });
    }

    // LAZY LOAD IMAGES
    function lazyLoadImages(images) {
      for(l=0; images.length > l; l++){
          var image = images[l];
          if (typeof image.dataset.lazySrc != "undefined") {
            if (image.src != image.dataset.lazySrc) {
              image.src = image.dataset.lazySrc;
            }
          }
        }
    }

    function lazyLoadEvent() {
      if ("" == "1") {
        var tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-button');
        if (tabs.length > 0) {
          for(i=0; tabs.length > i; i++){
            if (i == 0) {
              var targetIdOne     = tabs[i].dataset.target,
                  tabTargetOne       = document.getElementById(targetIdOne),
                  tabTargetOneImages = tabTargetOne.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetOneImages);
            }

            tabs[i].addEventListener('click', function() {
              var tabTargetId     = this.dataset.target,
                  tabTarget       = document.getElementById(tabTargetId),
                  tabTargetImages = tabTarget.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetImages);
            });
          }
        }
      }
    }

    compileTabTargets(tabs, tabTargets);
    tabClick(tabs, tabTargets);
    lazyLoadEvent();
    
  });
           </script>

            <script src="https://content.markitcdn.com/www.chartworks.io/content/chartworks/dist/1.4.8/js/chartworks.min.js" type="text/javascript">
            </script>
            <script>
             $('.index-name').bind('click', function() {
        var index       = $(this),
            indexRic    = index.attr('data-ric'),
            indices     = $('.index-data-container').find('.index-name'),
            indexTab    = index.find('.index-tab');

        for (i=0;indices.length > i;i++) {
            $(indices[i]).removeClass('active');
            $('.index-tab').removeClass('active');
        }
        index.addClass('active');
        indexTab.addClass('active');
        renderChart(window.chartworks_token, indexRic)
    });

    const first_ric = $('.index-name')[0].dataset.ric;

    function getChartData(obj) {
        window.chartworks_token = obj.access_token;
        renderChart(obj.access_token, first_ric);
    }

    
    function renderChart(token, ric) {

        // Set the chart inputs
        var chartInputs = {
          "symbol": ric,
          "realTime": false,
          "cultureCode": "en-US",
          "fontColor": "#999999",
          "fontSize": 18,
          "upperPanelHeight": 144,
          "lowerPanelHeight": 0,
          "numDays": 1,
          "priceLineColor": "#ff8000",
          "priceLineWidth": 3,
          "showVolume": false,
          "volumeColor": "#ff8000",
          "width": 556,
          "xGridLineColor": "#ffffff",
          "xGridLineWidth": 1,
          "yGridLineColor": "#dddddd",
          "yGridLineWidth": 1
        };

        // Stringify & Encode Inputs
        var encoded = encodeURIComponent(JSON.stringify(chartInputs, null));

        // Create API call
        var url = "https://api.markitondemand.com/apiman-gateway/MOD/chartworks-image/1/Chart/price?inputs=" + encoded + "&access_token=" + token;

        // Append to our target
        $(".index-data-container .index-chart img").remove();
        $('<img />').attr("src", url).appendTo(".index-data-container .index-chart");


    }
            </script>
            <script src="https://apiservice.reuters.com/api/service/modtoken?method=get&amp;format=json&amp;callback=getChartData&amp;apikey=72461C50B1CEAD3135BA6BDA53B203D3&amp;deviceid=E7CDD293-9C3A-5AB9-9181-58E1B572DD44" type="text/javascript">
            </script>

      <section class="module tab-markets-regional">
       <header class="module-header">
        <h4 class="module-heading">
         Regional Markets
         <span class="title-last">
          News
         </span>
        </h4>
       </header>
       <section class="module-content">
        <!-- TABS -->
        <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tab-table" id="regionMarketsTabs" width="100%">
         <tbody>
          <tr>
           <th class="tab-1 tab-button current" data-target="tab-markets-us" width="33.333333333333336%">
            United States
           </th>
           <th class="tab-2 tab-button" data-target="tab-markets-emea" width="33.333333333333336%">
            Europe &amp; Middle East
           </th>
           <th class="tab-3 tab-button" data-target="tab-markets-asia" width="33.333333333333336%">
            Asia Pacific
           </th>
          </tr>
         </tbody>
        </table>
        <style>
         .tab-markets-regional .tabs {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li span,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li span.hrefClone{
    background: none !important;
    border: none !important;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current{
    background: #f5f5f5 !important;
    padding-bottom: 0px !important;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current span{
    padding-bottom: 13px;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current span,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current span.hrefClone{
    font-family: knowledge-medium,helvetica,arial,sans-serif;
}
#tab-markets-us .news-headline-list,
#tab-markets-emea .news-headline-list,
#tab-markets-asia .news-headline-list{
    margin-bottom: 40px;
}
        </style>
       </section>
      </section>
      <script>
       $(function(){

    var tabs       = $('#regionMarketsTabs .tab-button');
    var tabTargets = []

    function compileTabTargets(tabs, targetsArray) {
      for (i=0; i < tabs.length; i++) {
        var tabTargetId = $(tabs[i]).data('target');
        var tabTarget   = $('#'+tabTargetId);
        targetsArray.push(tabTarget);
      }
    }

    function tabClick(tabs, targets) {
      tabs.on('click', function() {
        var targetId = $(this).data('target');
        var target   = $('#'+targetId);

        // SHOW / HIDE MODULES
        for (j=0; j < targets.length; j++) {
          var module = targets[j][0];

          if (targetId != module.id) {
            $(module).addClass('hidden');
          } else {
            $(module).removeClass('hidden');
          }
        }

        // ADD CURRENT CLASS TO TAB
        for (k=0; k < tabs.length; k++) {
          if (tabs[k] == this) {
            $(tabs[k]).addClass('current');
          } else {
            $(tabs[k]).removeClass('current');
          }
        }
      });
    }

    // LAZY LOAD IMAGES
    function lazyLoadImages(images) {
      for(l=0; images.length > l; l++){
          var image = images[l];
          if (typeof image.dataset.lazySrc != "undefined") {
            if (image.src != image.dataset.lazySrc) {
              image.src = image.dataset.lazySrc;
            }
          }
        }
    }

    function lazyLoadEvent() {
      if ("" == "1") {
        var tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-button');
        if (tabs.length > 0) {
          for(i=0; tabs.length > i; i++){
            if (i == 0) {
              var targetIdOne     = tabs[i].dataset.target,
                  tabTargetOne       = document.getElementById(targetIdOne),
                  tabTargetOneImages = tabTargetOne.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetOneImages);
            }

            tabs[i].addEventListener('click', function() {
              var tabTargetId     = this.dataset.target,
                  tabTarget       = document.getElementById(tabTargetId),
                  tabTargetImages = tabTarget.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetImages);
            });
          }
        }
      }
    }

    compileTabTargets(tabs, tabTargets);
    tabClick(tabs, tabTargets);
    lazyLoadEvent();
    
  });
      </script>
      <section class="module" id="tab-markets-us">
       <section class="module-content">
        <div class="news-headline-list medium">
         <article class="story">
          <div class="story-content">

            <h3 class="story-title">

           <script>
            $(function(){

    var tabs       = $('#marketsModuleTabs .tab-button');
    var tabTargets = []

    function compileTabTargets(tabs, targetsArray) {
      for (i=0; i < tabs.length; i++) {
        var tabTargetId = $(tabs[i]).data('target');
        var tabTarget   = $('#'+tabTargetId);
        targetsArray.push(tabTarget);
      }
    }

    function tabClick(tabs, targets) {
      tabs.on('click', function() {
        var targetId = $(this).data('target');
        var target   = $('#'+targetId);

        // SHOW / HIDE MODULES
        for (j=0; j < targets.length; j++) {
          var module = targets[j][0];

          if (targetId != module.id) {
            $(module).addClass('hidden');
          } else {
            $(module).removeClass('hidden');
          }
        }

        // ADD CURRENT CLASS TO TAB
        for (k=0; k < tabs.length; k++) {
          if (tabs[k] == this) {
            $(tabs[k]).addClass('current');
          } else {
            $(tabs[k]).removeClass('current');
          }
        }
      });
    }

    // LAZY LOAD IMAGES
    function lazyLoadImages(images) {
      for(l=0; images.length > l; l++){
          var image = images[l];
          if (typeof image.dataset.lazySrc != "undefined") {
            if (image.src != image.dataset.lazySrc) {
              image.src = image.dataset.lazySrc;
            }
          }
        }
    }

    function lazyLoadEvent() {
      if ("" == "1") {
        var tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-button');
        if (tabs.length > 0) {
          for(i=0; tabs.length > i; i++){
            if (i == 0) {
              var targetIdOne     = tabs[i].dataset.target,
                  tabTargetOne       = document.getElementById(targetIdOne),
                  tabTargetOneImages = tabTargetOne.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetOneImages);
            }

            tabs[i].addEventListener('click', function() {
              var tabTargetId     = this.dataset.target,
                  tabTarget       = document.getElementById(tabTargetId),
                  tabTargetImages = tabTarget.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetImages);
            });
          }
        }
      }
    }

    compileTabTargets(tabs, tabTargets);
    tabClick(tabs, tabTargets);
    lazyLoadEvent();
    
  });
           </script>

            <script src="https://content.markitcdn.com/www.chartworks.io/content/chartworks/dist/1.4.8/js/chartworks.min.js" type="text/javascript">
            </script>
            <script>
             $('.index-name').bind('click', function() {
        var index       = $(this),
            indexRic    = index.attr('data-ric'),
            indices     = $('.index-data-container').find('.index-name'),
            indexTab    = index.find('.index-tab');

        for (i=0;indices.length > i;i++) {
            $(indices[i]).removeClass('active');
            $('.index-tab').removeClass('active');
        }
        index.addClass('active');
        indexTab.addClass('active');
        renderChart(window.chartworks_token, indexRic)
    });

    const first_ric = $('.index-name')[0].dataset.ric;

    function getChartData(obj) {
        window.chartworks_token = obj.access_token;
        renderChart(obj.access_token, first_ric);
    }

    
    function renderChart(token, ric) {

        // Set the chart inputs
        var chartInputs = {
          "symbol": ric,
          "realTime": false,
          "cultureCode": "en-US",
          "fontColor": "#999999",
          "fontSize": 18,
          "upperPanelHeight": 144,
          "lowerPanelHeight": 0,
          "numDays": 1,
          "priceLineColor": "#ff8000",
          "priceLineWidth": 3,
          "showVolume": false,
          "volumeColor": "#ff8000",
          "width": 556,
          "xGridLineColor": "#ffffff",
          "xGridLineWidth": 1,
          "yGridLineColor": "#dddddd",
          "yGridLineWidth": 1
        };

        // Stringify & Encode Inputs
        var encoded = encodeURIComponent(JSON.stringify(chartInputs, null));

        // Create API call
        var url = "https://api.markitondemand.com/apiman-gateway/MOD/chartworks-image/1/Chart/price?inputs=" + encoded + "&access_token=" + token;

        // Append to our target
        $(".index-data-container .index-chart img").remove();
        $('<img />').attr("src", url).appendTo(".index-data-container .index-chart");


    }
            </script>
            <script src="https://apiservice.reuters.com/api/service/modtoken?method=get&amp;format=json&amp;callback=getChartData&amp;apikey=72461C50B1CEAD3135BA6BDA53B203D3&amp;deviceid=E7CDD293-9C3A-5AB9-9181-58E1B572DD44" type="text/javascript">
            </script>

    if((TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("us.reuters") > -1) || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("uk.reuters") > -1) || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("jp.reuters") > -1) || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("lta.reuters") > -1)){

        {displayAd_sync_fastlane(dz_final,  "storychannel=" + Reuters.info.channel + ";" + adParams2 + "" );}
        else{ displayAd_sync_fastlane( dz_final, "" + adParams2 + "" ); }

        { displayAd_sync(dz_final,  "storychannel=" + Reuters.info.channel + ";" + adParams2 + "");}
        else{ displayAd_sync( dz_final, "" + adParams2 + "" ); }

         <span class="title-last">

       <section class="module-content">
        <!-- TABS -->
        <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tab-table" id="regionMarketsTabs" width="100%">
         <tbody>
          <tr>
           <th class="tab-1 tab-button current" data-target="tab-markets-us" width="33.333333333333336%">
            United States
           </th>
           <th class="tab-2 tab-button" data-target="tab-markets-emea" width="33.333333333333336%">

           </th>
           <th class="tab-3 tab-button" data-target="tab-markets-asia" width="33.333333333333336%">
            Asia Pacific
           </th>
          </tr>
         </tbody>
        </table>
        <style>
         .tab-markets-regional .tabs {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li span,

    padding-bottom: 0px !important;
}

    padding-bottom: 13px;
}

    font-family: knowledge-medium,helvetica,arial,sans-serif;
}
#tab-markets-us .news-headline-list,

#tab-markets-asia .news-headline-list{
    margin-bottom: 40px;
}
        </style>
       </section>
      </section>
      <script>
       $(function(){

    var tabs       = $('#regionMarketsTabs .tab-button');
    var tabTargets = []

    function compileTabTargets(tabs, targetsArray) {
      for (i=0; i < tabs.length; i++) {
        var tabTargetId = $(tabs[i]).data('target');
        var tabTarget   = $('#'+tabTargetId);
        targetsArray.push(tabTarget);
      }
    }

    function tabClick(tabs, targets) {
      tabs.on('click', function() {
        var targetId = $(this).data('target');
        var target   = $('#'+targetId);

        // SHOW / HIDE MODULES
        for (j=0; j < targets.length; j++) {
          var module = targets[j][0];

          if (targetId != module.id) {
            $(module).addClass('hidden');
          } else {
            $(module).removeClass('hidden');
          }
        }

        // ADD CURRENT CLASS TO TAB
        for (k=0; k < tabs.length; k++) {
          if (tabs[k] == this) {
            $(tabs[k]).addClass('current');
          } else {
            $(tabs[k]).removeClass('current');
          }
        }
      });
    }

    // LAZY LOAD IMAGES
    function lazyLoadImages(images) {
      for(l=0; images.length > l; l++){
          var image = images[l];
          if (typeof image.dataset.lazySrc != "undefined") {
            if (image.src != image.dataset.lazySrc) {
              image.src = image.dataset.lazySrc;
            }
          }
        }
    }

    function lazyLoadEvent() {
      if ("" == "1") {
        var tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-button');
        if (tabs.length > 0) {
          for(i=0; tabs.length > i; i++){
            if (i == 0) {
              var targetIdOne     = tabs[i].dataset.target,
                  tabTargetOne       = document.getElementById(targetIdOne),
                  tabTargetOneImages = tabTargetOne.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetOneImages);
            }

            tabs[i].addEventListener('click', function() {
              var tabTargetId     = this.dataset.target,
                  tabTarget       = document.getElementById(tabTargetId),
                  tabTargetImages = tabTarget.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetImages);
            });
          }
        }
      }
    }

    compileTabTargets(tabs, tabTargets);
    tabClick(tabs, tabTargets);
    lazyLoadEvent();
    
  });
      </script>

           <script>
            $(function(){

    var tabs       = $('#marketsModuleTabs .tab-button');
    var tabTargets = []

    function compileTabTargets(tabs, targetsArray) {
      for (i=0; i < tabs.length; i++) {
        var tabTargetId = $(tabs[i]).data('target');
        var tabTarget   = $('#'+tabTargetId);
        targetsArray.push(tabTarget);
      }
    }

    function tabClick(tabs, targets) {
      tabs.on('click', function() {
        var targetId = $(this).data('target');
        var target   = $('#'+targetId);

        // SHOW / HIDE MODULES
        for (j=0; j < targets.length; j++) {
          var module = targets[j][0];

          if (targetId != module.id) {
            $(module).addClass('hidden');
          } else {
            $(module).removeClass('hidden');
          }
        }

        // ADD CURRENT CLASS TO TAB
        for (k=0; k < tabs.length; k++) {
          if (tabs[k] == this) {
            $(tabs[k]).addClass('current');
          } else {
            $(tabs[k]).removeClass('current');
          }
        }
      });
    }

    // LAZY LOAD IMAGES
    function lazyLoadImages(images) {
      for(l=0; images.length > l; l++){
          var image = images[l];
          if (typeof image.dataset.lazySrc != "undefined") {
            if (image.src != image.dataset.lazySrc) {
              image.src = image.dataset.lazySrc;
            }
          }
        }
    }

    function lazyLoadEvent() {
      if ("" == "1") {
        var tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-button');
        if (tabs.length > 0) {
          for(i=0; tabs.length > i; i++){
            if (i == 0) {
              var targetIdOne     = tabs[i].dataset.target,
                  tabTargetOne       = document.getElementById(targetIdOne),
                  tabTargetOneImages = tabTargetOne.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetOneImages);
            }

            tabs[i].addEventListener('click', function() {
              var tabTargetId     = this.dataset.target,
                  tabTarget       = document.getElementById(tabTargetId),
                  tabTargetImages = tabTarget.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetImages);
            });
          }
        }
      }
    }

    compileTabTargets(tabs, tabTargets);
    tabClick(tabs, tabTargets);
    lazyLoadEvent();
    
  });
           </script>

            <script src="https://content.markitcdn.com/www.chartworks.io/content/chartworks/dist/1.4.8/js/chartworks.min.js" type="text/javascript">
            </script>
            <script>
             $('.index-name').bind('click', function() {
        var index       = $(this),
            indexRic    = index.attr('data-ric'),
            indices     = $('.index-data-container').find('.index-name'),
            indexTab    = index.find('.index-tab');

        for (i=0;indices.length > i;i++) {
            $(indices[i]).removeClass('active');
            $('.index-tab').removeClass('active');
        }
        index.addClass('active');
        indexTab.addClass('active');
        renderChart(window.chartworks_token, indexRic)
    });

    const first_ric = $('.index-name')[0].dataset.ric;

    function getChartData(obj) {
        window.chartworks_token = obj.access_token;
        renderChart(obj.access_token, first_ric);
    }

    
    function renderChart(token, ric) {

        // Set the chart inputs
        var chartInputs = {
          "symbol": ric,
          "realTime": false,
          "cultureCode": "en-US",
          "fontColor": "#999999",
          "fontSize": 18,
          "upperPanelHeight": 144,
          "lowerPanelHeight": 0,
          "numDays": 1,
          "priceLineColor": "#ff8000",
          "priceLineWidth": 3,
          "showVolume": false,
          "volumeColor": "#ff8000",
          "width": 556,
          "xGridLineColor": "#ffffff",
          "xGridLineWidth": 1,
          "yGridLineColor": "#dddddd",
          "yGridLineWidth": 1
        };

        // Stringify & Encode Inputs
        var encoded = encodeURIComponent(JSON.stringify(chartInputs, null));

        // Create API call
        var url = "https://api.markitondemand.com/apiman-gateway/MOD/chartworks-image/1/Chart/price?inputs=" + encoded + "&access_token=" + token;

        // Append to our target
        $(".index-data-container .index-chart img").remove();
        $('<img />').attr("src", url).appendTo(".index-data-container .index-chart");


    }
            </script>
            <script src="https://apiservice.reuters.com/api/service/modtoken?method=get&amp;format=json&amp;callback=getChartData&amp;apikey=72461C50B1CEAD3135BA6BDA53B203D3&amp;deviceid=E7CDD293-9C3A-5AB9-9181-58E1B572DD44" type="text/javascript">
            </script>

    } else{ displayAd("div_gpt_lb_low", dz_final, [[728, 90],[970,250],[970,90],[970,66],[1,1]], "type=leaderboardlow;" + adParams2 + "" ); }

.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li span,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li span.hrefClone{
    background: none !important;
    border: none !important;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current{
    background: #f5f5f5 !important;
    padding-bottom: 0px !important;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current span{
    padding-bottom: 13px;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current span,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current span.hrefClone{
    font-family: knowledge-medium,helvetica,arial,sans-serif;
}
#tab-markets-us .news-headline-list,
#tab-markets-emea .news-headline-list,
#tab-markets-asia .news-headline-list{
    margin-bottom: 40px;
}
        </style>
       </section>
      </section>
      <script>
       $(function(){

    var tabs       = $('#regionMarketsTabs .tab-button');
    var tabTargets = []

    function compileTabTargets(tabs, targetsArray) {
      for (i=0; i < tabs.length; i++) {
        var tabTargetId = $(tabs[i]).data('target');
        var tabTarget   = $('#'+tabTargetId);
        targetsArray.push(tabTarget);
      }
    }

    function tabClick(tabs, targets) {
      tabs.on('click', function() {
        var targetId = $(this).data('target');
        var target   = $('#'+targetId);

        // SHOW / HIDE MODULES
        for (j=0; j < targets.length; j++) {
          var module = targets[j][0];

          if (targetId != module.id) {
            $(module).addClass('hidden');
          } else {
            $(module).removeClass('hidden');
          }
        }

        // ADD CURRENT CLASS TO TAB
        for (k=0; k < tabs.length; k++) {
          if (tabs[k] == this) {
            $(tabs[k]).addClass('current');
          } else {
            $(tabs[k]).removeClass('current');
          }
        }
      });
    }

    // LAZY LOAD IMAGES
    function lazyLoadImages(images) {
      for(l=0; images.length > l; l++){
          var image = images[l];
          if (typeof image.dataset.lazySrc != "undefined") {
            if (image.src != image.dataset.lazySrc) {
              image.src = image.dataset.lazySrc;
            }
          }
        }
    }

    function lazyLoadEvent() {
      if ("" == "1") {
        var tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-button');
        if (tabs.length > 0) {
          for(i=0; tabs.length > i; i++){
            if (i == 0) {
              var targetIdOne     = tabs[i].dataset.target,
                  tabTargetOne       = document.getElementById(targetIdOne),
                  tabTargetOneImages = tabTargetOne.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetOneImages);
            }

            tabs[i].addEventListener('click', function() {
              var tabTargetId     = this.dataset.target,
                  tabTarget       = document.getElementById(tabTargetId),
                  tabTargetImages = tabTarget.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetImages);
            });
          }
        }
      }
    }

    compileTabTargets(tabs, tabTargets);
    tabClick(tabs, tabTargets);
    lazyLoadEvent();
    
  });
      </script>

           <script>
            $(function(){

    var tabs       = $('#marketsModuleTabs .tab-button');
    var tabTargets = []

    function compileTabTargets(tabs, targetsArray) {
      for (i=0; i < tabs.length; i++) {
        var tabTargetId = $(tabs[i]).data('target');
        var tabTarget   = $('#'+tabTargetId);
        targetsArray.push(tabTarget);
      }
    }

    function tabClick(tabs, targets) {
      tabs.on('click', function() {
        var targetId = $(this).data('target');
        var target   = $('#'+targetId);

        // SHOW / HIDE MODULES
        for (j=0; j < targets.length; j++) {
          var module = targets[j][0];

          if (targetId != module.id) {
            $(module).addClass('hidden');
          } else {
            $(module).removeClass('hidden');
          }
        }

        // ADD CURRENT CLASS TO TAB
        for (k=0; k < tabs.length; k++) {
          if (tabs[k] == this) {
            $(tabs[k]).addClass('current');
          } else {
            $(tabs[k]).removeClass('current');
          }
        }
      });
    }

    // LAZY LOAD IMAGES
    function lazyLoadImages(images) {
      for(l=0; images.length > l; l++){
          var image = images[l];
          if (typeof image.dataset.lazySrc != "undefined") {
            if (image.src != image.dataset.lazySrc) {
              image.src = image.dataset.lazySrc;
            }
          }
        }
    }

    function lazyLoadEvent() {
      if ("" == "1") {
        var tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-button');
        if (tabs.length > 0) {
          for(i=0; tabs.length > i; i++){
            if (i == 0) {
              var targetIdOne     = tabs[i].dataset.target,
                  tabTargetOne       = document.getElementById(targetIdOne),
                  tabTargetOneImages = tabTargetOne.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetOneImages);
            }

            tabs[i].addEventListener('click', function() {
              var tabTargetId     = this.dataset.target,
                  tabTarget       = document.getElementById(tabTargetId),
                  tabTargetImages = tabTarget.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetImages);
            });
          }
        }
      }
    }

    compileTabTargets(tabs, tabTargets);
    tabClick(tabs, tabTargets);
    lazyLoadEvent();
    
  });
           </script>

            <script src="https://content.markitcdn.com/www.chartworks.io/content/chartworks/dist/1.4.8/js/chartworks.min.js" type="text/javascript">
            </script>
            <script>
             $('.index-name').bind('click', function() {
        var index       = $(this),
            indexRic    = index.attr('data-ric'),
            indices     = $('.index-data-container').find('.index-name'),
            indexTab    = index.find('.index-tab');

        for (i=0;indices.length > i;i++) {
            $(indices[i]).removeClass('active');
            $('.index-tab').removeClass('active');
        }
        index.addClass('active');
        indexTab.addClass('active');
        renderChart(window.chartworks_token, indexRic)
    });

    const first_ric = $('.index-name')[0].dataset.ric;

    function getChartData(obj) {
        window.chartworks_token = obj.access_token;
        renderChart(obj.access_token, first_ric);
    }

    
    function renderChart(token, ric) {

        // Set the chart inputs
        var chartInputs = {
          "symbol": ric,
          "realTime": false,
          "cultureCode": "en-US",
          "fontColor": "#999999",
          "fontSize": 18,
          "upperPanelHeight": 144,
          "lowerPanelHeight": 0,
          "numDays": 1,
          "priceLineColor": "#ff8000",
          "priceLineWidth": 3,
          "showVolume": false,
          "volumeColor": "#ff8000",
          "width": 556,
          "xGridLineColor": "#ffffff",
          "xGridLineWidth": 1,
          "yGridLineColor": "#dddddd",
          "yGridLineWidth": 1
        };

        // Stringify & Encode Inputs
        var encoded = encodeURIComponent(JSON.stringify(chartInputs, null));

        // Create API call
        var url = "https://api.markitondemand.com/apiman-gateway/MOD/chartworks-image/1/Chart/price?inputs=" + encoded + "&access_token=" + token;

        // Append to our target
        $(".index-data-container .index-chart img").remove();
        $('<img />').attr("src", url).appendTo(".index-data-container .index-chart");


    }
            </script>
            <script src="https://apiservice.reuters.com/api/service/modtoken?method=get&amp;format=json&amp;callback=getChartData&amp;apikey=72461C50B1CEAD3135BA6BDA53B203D3&amp;deviceid=E7CDD293-9C3A-5AB9-9181-58E1B572DD44" type="text/javascript">
            </script>

      <div class="ad" id="leaderboardlow">
       <script type="text/javascript">
        var dz_final = TR3.extractDartZone();
// leaderboard
if( 'leaderboardlow' == 'leaderboard'){
    //US/UK HOME FASTLANE
    if((TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("us.reuters") > -1) || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("uk.reuters") > -1) || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("jp.reuters") > -1) || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("lta.reuters") > -1)){
        if(typeof(Reuters)!='undefined' && typeof(Reuters.info)!='undefined' && typeof(Reuters.info.channel)!='undefined')
        {displayAd_sync_fastlane(dz_final,  "storychannel=" + Reuters.info.channel + ";" + adParams2 + "" );}
        else{ displayAd_sync_fastlane( dz_final, "" + adParams2 + "" ); }
    }
    else{ 
		if(typeof(Reuters)!='undefined' && typeof(Reuters.info)!='undefined' && typeof(Reuters.info.channel)!='undefined')
        { displayAd_sync(dz_final,  "storychannel=" + Reuters.info.channel + ";" + adParams2 + "");}
        else{ displayAd_sync( dz_final, "" + adParams2 + "" ); }
    }
}
else if('leaderboardlow' == 'mpu'){ googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('div_gpt_mpu'); }); }
else if('leaderboardlow' == 'mpu2'){ googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('div_gpt_mpu2'); }); }
else if('leaderboardlow' == 'mpulow'){ googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('div_gpt_mpulow'); }); }
else if('leaderboardlow' == 'leaderboardcenter'){

    <div class="group wrap" id="rcs-sectionMain">
     <div class="column1 col col-10">
      <div class="olympics-topStory">
       <section>
        <div class="group" id="">
         <div class="column1 col col-6">
          <div class="gridPanel grid5">
           <div class="module">
            <div class="moduleBody">
             <div class="topStory">
              <div class="photo">
               <a href="/article/us-usa-stocks/wall-street-crawls-to-record-levels-on-trade-hopes-idUSKBN1Y01HD">
                <img alt="Photo" border="0" src="https://s3.reutersmedia.net/resources/r/?m=02&amp;d=20191126&amp;t=2&amp;i=1456994439&amp;w=430&amp;fh=&amp;fw=&amp;ll=&amp;pl=&amp;sq=&amp;r=LYNXMPEFAP12Q"/>
               </a>
              </div>
              <h2>
               <a href="/article/us-usa-stocks/wall-street-crawls-to-record-levels-on-trade-hopes-idUSKBN1Y01HD">
                Wall Street crawls to record levels on trade hopes
               </a>
              </h2>
              <p>
               NEW YORK U.S. stocks crawled higher on Tuesday, and all three major Wall Street indexes notched record levels, as upbeat comments by President Donald Trump on trade talks eclipsed some softer-than-anticipated economic data. |
               <span class="inlineLinks">
                <a href="/video/2019/11/26/wall-street-climbs-to-records?videoId=632622846&amp;newsChannel=ousivMolt">
                 Video
                </a>
               </span>
              </p>
             </div>

      <section class="module tab-markets-regional">
       <header class="module-header">
        <h4 class="module-heading">
         Regional Markets
         <span class="title-last">
          News
         </span>
        </h4>
       </header>
       <section class="module-content">
        <!-- TABS -->
        <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tab-table" id="regionMarketsTabs" width="100%">
         <tbody>
          <tr>
           <th class="tab-1 tab-button current" data-target="tab-markets-us" width="33.333333333333336%">
            United States
           </th>
           <th class="tab-2 tab-button" data-target="tab-markets-emea" width="33.333333333333336%">
            Europe &amp; Middle East
           </th>
           <th class="tab-3 tab-button" data-target="tab-markets-asia" width="33.333333333333336%">
            Asia Pacific
           </th>
          </tr>
         </tbody>
        </table>
        <style>
         .tab-markets-regional .tabs {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li span,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li span.hrefClone{
    background: none !important;
    border: none !important;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current{
    background: #f5f5f5 !important;
    padding-bottom: 0px !important;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current span{
    padding-bottom: 13px;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current span,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current span.hrefClone{
    font-family: knowledge-medium,helvetica,arial,sans-serif;
}
#tab-markets-us .news-headline-list,
#tab-markets-emea .news-headline-list,
#tab-markets-asia .news-headline-list{
    margin-bottom: 40px;
}
        </style>
       </section>
      </section>
      <script>
       $(function(){

    var tabs       = $('#regionMarketsTabs .tab-button');
    var tabTargets = []

    function compileTabTargets(tabs, targetsArray) {
      for (i=0; i < tabs.length; i++) {
        var tabTargetId = $(tabs[i]).data('target');
        var tabTarget   = $('#'+tabTargetId);
        targetsArray.push(tabTarget);
      }
    }

    function tabClick(tabs, targets) {
      tabs.on('click', function() {
        var targetId = $(this).data('target');
        var target   = $('#'+targetId);

        // SHOW / HIDE MODULES
        for (j=0; j < targets.length; j++) {
          var module = targets[j][0];

          if (targetId != module.id) {
            $(module).addClass('hidden');
          } else {
            $(module).removeClass('hidden');
          }
        }

        // ADD CURRENT CLASS TO TAB
        for (k=0; k < tabs.length; k++) {
          if (tabs[k] == this) {
            $(tabs[k]).addClass('current');
          } else {
            $(tabs[k]).removeClass('current');
          }
        }
      });
    }

    // LAZY LOAD IMAGES
    function lazyLoadImages(images) {
      for(l=0; images.length > l; l++){
          var image = images[l];
          if (typeof image.dataset.lazySrc != "undefined") {
            if (image.src != image.dataset.lazySrc) {
              image.src = image.dataset.lazySrc;
            }
          }
        }
    }

    function lazyLoadEvent() {
      if ("" == "1") {
        var tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-button');
        if (tabs.length > 0) {
          for(i=0; tabs.length > i; i++){
            if (i == 0) {
              var targetIdOne     = tabs[i].dataset.target,
                  tabTargetOne       = document.getElementById(targetIdOne),
                  tabTargetOneImages = tabTargetOne.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetOneImages);
            }

            tabs[i].addEventListener('click', function() {
              var tabTargetId     = this.dataset.target,
                  tabTarget       = document.getElementById(tabTargetId),
                  tabTargetImages = tabTarget.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetImages);
            });
          }
        }
      }
    }

    compileTabTargets(tabs, tabTargets);
    tabClick(tabs, tabTargets);
    lazyLoadEvent();
    
  });
      </script>

             <!-- TABS -->
             <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tab-table blend small" id="marketsModuleTabs" width="100%">
              <tbody>
               <tr>
                <th class="tab-1 tab-button current" data-target="leadstocks" width="25.0%">
                 STOCKS
                </th>
                <th class="tab-2 tab-button" data-target="leadbonds" width="25.0%">
                 BONDS
                </th>
                <th class="tab-3 tab-button" data-target="leadcurrencies" width="25.0%">

           <script>
            $(function(){

    var tabs       = $('#marketsModuleTabs .tab-button');
    var tabTargets = []

    function compileTabTargets(tabs, targetsArray) {
      for (i=0; i < tabs.length; i++) {
        var tabTargetId = $(tabs[i]).data('target');
        var tabTarget   = $('#'+tabTargetId);
        targetsArray.push(tabTarget);
      }
    }

    function tabClick(tabs, targets) {
      tabs.on('click', function() {
        var targetId = $(this).data('target');
        var target   = $('#'+targetId);

        // SHOW / HIDE MODULES
        for (j=0; j < targets.length; j++) {
          var module = targets[j][0];

          if (targetId != module.id) {
            $(module).addClass('hidden');
          } else {
            $(module).removeClass('hidden');
          }
        }

        // ADD CURRENT CLASS TO TAB
        for (k=0; k < tabs.length; k++) {
          if (tabs[k] == this) {
            $(tabs[k]).addClass('current');
          } else {
            $(tabs[k]).removeClass('current');
          }
        }
      });
    }

    // LAZY LOAD IMAGES
    function lazyLoadImages(images) {
      for(l=0; images.length > l; l++){
          var image = images[l];
          if (typeof image.dataset.lazySrc != "undefined") {
            if (image.src != image.dataset.lazySrc) {
              image.src = image.dataset.lazySrc;
            }
          }
        }
    }

    function lazyLoadEvent() {
      if ("" == "1") {
        var tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-button');
        if (tabs.length > 0) {
          for(i=0; tabs.length > i; i++){
            if (i == 0) {
              var targetIdOne     = tabs[i].dataset.target,
                  tabTargetOne       = document.getElementById(targetIdOne),
                  tabTargetOneImages = tabTargetOne.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetOneImages);
            }

            tabs[i].addEventListener('click', function() {
              var tabTargetId     = this.dataset.target,
                  tabTarget       = document.getElementById(tabTargetId),
                  tabTargetImages = tabTarget.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetImages);
            });
          }
        }
      }
    }

    compileTabTargets(tabs, tabTargets);
    tabClick(tabs, tabTargets);
    lazyLoadEvent();
    
  });
           </script>

            <script src="https://content.markitcdn.com/www.chartworks.io/content/chartworks/dist/1.4.8/js/chartworks.min.js" type="text/javascript">
            </script>
            <script>
             $('.index-name').bind('click', function() {
        var index       = $(this),
            indexRic    = index.attr('data-ric'),
            indices     = $('.index-data-container').find('.index-name'),
            indexTab    = index.find('.index-tab');

        for (i=0;indices.length > i;i++) {
            $(indices[i]).removeClass('active');
            $('.index-tab').removeClass('active');
        }
        index.addClass('active');
        indexTab.addClass('active');
        renderChart(window.chartworks_token, indexRic)
    });

    const first_ric = $('.index-name')[0].dataset.ric;

    function getChartData(obj) {
        window.chartworks_token = obj.access_token;
        renderChart(obj.access_token, first_ric);
    }

    
    function renderChart(token, ric) {

        // Set the chart inputs
        var chartInputs = {
          "symbol": ric,
          "realTime": false,
          "cultureCode": "en-US",
          "fontColor": "#999999",
          "fontSize": 18,
          "upperPanelHeight": 144,
          "lowerPanelHeight": 0,
          "numDays": 1,
          "priceLineColor": "#ff8000",
          "priceLineWidth": 3,
          "showVolume": false,
          "volumeColor": "#ff8000",
          "width": 556,
          "xGridLineColor": "#ffffff",
          "xGridLineWidth": 1,
          "yGridLineColor": "#dddddd",
          "yGridLineWidth": 1
        };

        // Stringify & Encode Inputs
        var encoded = encodeURIComponent(JSON.stringify(chartInputs, null));

        // Create API call
        var url = "https://api.markitondemand.com/apiman-gateway/MOD/chartworks-image/1/Chart/price?inputs=" + encoded + "&access_token=" + token;

        // Append to our target
        $(".index-data-container .index-chart img").remove();
        $('<img />').attr("src", url).appendTo(".index-data-container .index-chart");


    }
            </script>
            <script src="https://apiservice.reuters.com/api/service/modtoken?method=get&amp;format=json&amp;callback=getChartData&amp;apikey=72461C50B1CEAD3135BA6BDA53B203D3&amp;deviceid=E7CDD293-9C3A-5AB9-9181-58E1B572DD44" type="text/javascript">
            </script>

     <div class="ad-sponsor-page">

       <div class="ad" id="sponsorlogo">
        <script type="text/javascript">
         var dz_final = TR3.extractDartZone();
// leaderboard
if( 'sponsorlogo' == 'leaderboard'){
    //US/UK HOME FASTLANE
    if((TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("us.reuters") > -1) || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("uk.reuters") > -1) || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("jp.reuters") > -1) || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("lta.reuters") > -1)){
        if(typeof(Reuters)!='undefined' && typeof(Reuters.info)!='undefined' && typeof(Reuters.info.channel)!='undefined')
        {displayAd_sync_fastlane(dz_final,  "storychannel=" + Reuters.info.channel + ";" + adParams2 + "" );}
        else{ displayAd_sync_fastlane( dz_final, "" + adParams2 + "" ); }
    }
    else{ 
		if(typeof(Reuters)!='undefined' && typeof(Reuters.info)!='undefined' && typeof(Reuters.info.channel)!='undefined')
        { displayAd_sync(dz_final,  "storychannel=" + Reuters.info.channel + ";" + adParams2 + "");}
        else{ displayAd_sync( dz_final, "" + adParams2 + "" ); }
    }
}
else if('sponsorlogo' == 'mpu'){ googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('div_gpt_mpu'); }); }
else if('sponsorlogo' == 'mpu2'){ googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('div_gpt_mpu2'); }); }
else if('sponsorlogo' == 'mpulow'){ googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('div_gpt_mpulow'); }); }
else if('sponsorlogo' == 'leaderboardcenter'){
    if((TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("us.reuters") > -1) || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("uk.reuters") > -1) || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("jp.reuters") > -1)  || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("lta.reuters") > -1)){ googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('div_gpt_lb_center'); }); }
    else{ displayAd("div_gpt_sponsorlogo", dz_final,  [250,36], "type=sponsorlogo;" + adParams2 + "" ); }
}
else if('sponsorlogo' == 'leaderboardlow'){
        if((TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("us.reuters") > -1) || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("uk.reuters") > -1) || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("jp.reuters") > -1) || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("lta.reuters") > -1)){ googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('div_gpt_lb_low'); }); }
        else{ displayAd("div_gpt_sponsorlogo", dz_final,  [250,36], "type=sponsorlogo;" + adParams2 + "" ); }
}
else{
    if(typeof(Reuters)!='undefined' && typeof(Reuters.info)!='undefined' && typeof(Reuters.info.channel)!='undefined'){
        displayAd("div_gpt_sponsorlogo", dz_final,  [250,36], "type=sponsorlogo;storychannel=" + Reuters.info.channel+ ";" + adParams2 + "" );
    } else{ displayAd("div_gpt_sponsorlogo", dz_final,  [250,36], "type=sponsorlogo;" + adParams2 + "" ); }	
}

    <div class="group wrap" id="rcs-sectionMain">
     <div class="column1 col col-10">
      <div class="olympics-topStory">
       <section>
        <div class="group" id="">
         <div class="column1 col col-6">
          <div class="gridPanel grid5">
           <div class="module">
            <div class="moduleBody">

        <!-- TABS -->
        <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tab-table" id="regionMarketsTabs" width="100%">
         <tbody>
          <tr>
           <th class="tab-1 tab-button current" data-target="tab-markets-us" width="33.333333333333336%">
            United States
           </th>
           <th class="tab-2 tab-button" data-target="tab-markets-emea" width="33.333333333333336%">

           </th>

            Asia Pacific

         </tbody>
        </table>
        <style>
         .tab-markets-regional .tabs {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li span,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li span.hrefClone{
    background: none !important;
    border: none !important;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current{
    background: #f5f5f5 !important;
    padding-bottom: 0px !important;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current span{
    padding-bottom: 13px;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current span,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current span.hrefClone{
    font-family: knowledge-medium,helvetica,arial,sans-serif;
}
#tab-markets-us .news-headline-list,

#tab-markets-asia .news-headline-list{
    margin-bottom: 40px;
}
        </style>
       </section>
      </section>
      <script>
       $(function(){

    var tabs       = $('#regionMarketsTabs .tab-button');
    var tabTargets = []

    function compileTabTargets(tabs, targetsArray) {
      for (i=0; i < tabs.length; i++) {
        var tabTargetId = $(tabs[i]).data('target');
        var tabTarget   = $('#'+tabTargetId);
        targetsArray.push(tabTarget);
      }
    }

    function tabClick(tabs, targets) {
      tabs.on('click', function() {
        var targetId = $(this).data('target');
        var target   = $('#'+targetId);

        // SHOW / HIDE MODULES
        for (j=0; j < targets.length; j++) {
          var module = targets[j][0];

          if (targetId != module.id) {
            $(module).addClass('hidden');
          } else {
            $(module).removeClass('hidden');
          }
        }

        // ADD CURRENT CLASS TO TAB
        for (k=0; k < tabs.length; k++) {
          if (tabs[k] == this) {
            $(tabs[k]).addClass('current');
          } else {
            $(tabs[k]).removeClass('current');
          }
        }
      });
    }

    // LAZY LOAD IMAGES
    function lazyLoadImages(images) {
      for(l=0; images.length > l; l++){
          var image = images[l];
          if (typeof image.dataset.lazySrc != "undefined") {
            if (image.src != image.dataset.lazySrc) {
              image.src = image.dataset.lazySrc;
            }
          }
        }
    }

    function lazyLoadEvent() {
      if ("" == "1") {
        var tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-button');
        if (tabs.length > 0) {
          for(i=0; tabs.length > i; i++){
            if (i == 0) {
              var targetIdOne     = tabs[i].dataset.target,
                  tabTargetOne       = document.getElementById(targetIdOne),
                  tabTargetOneImages = tabTargetOne.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetOneImages);
            }

            tabs[i].addEventListener('click', function() {
              var tabTargetId     = this.dataset.target,
                  tabTarget       = document.getElementById(tabTargetId),
                  tabTargetImages = tabTarget.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetImages);
            });
          }
        }
      }
    }

    compileTabTargets(tabs, tabTargets);
    tabClick(tabs, tabTargets);
    lazyLoadEvent();
    
  });
      </script>

             <!-- TABS -->
             <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tab-table blend small" id="marketsModuleTabs" width="100%">
              <tbody>
               <tr>
                <th class="tab-1 tab-button current" data-target="leadstocks" width="25.0%">
                 STOCKS
                </th>
                <th class="tab-2 tab-button" data-target="leadbonds" width="25.0%">
                 BONDS
                </th>
                <th class="tab-3 tab-button" data-target="leadcurrencies" width="25.0%">
                 CURRENCIES
                </th>
                <th class="tab-4 tab-button" data-target="leadcommodities" width="25.0%">
                 COMMODITIES
                </th>
               </tr>
              </tbody>
             </table>
            </section>
           </section>
           <script>
            $(function(){

    var tabs       = $('#marketsModuleTabs .tab-button');
    var tabTargets = []

    function compileTabTargets(tabs, targetsArray) {
      for (i=0; i < tabs.length; i++) {
        var tabTargetId = $(tabs[i]).data('target');
        var tabTarget   = $('#'+tabTargetId);
        targetsArray.push(tabTarget);
      }
    }

    function tabClick(tabs, targets) {
      tabs.on('click', function() {
        var targetId = $(this).data('target');
        var target   = $('#'+targetId);

        // SHOW / HIDE MODULES
        for (j=0; j < targets.length; j++) {
          var module = targets[j][0];

          if (targetId != module.id) {
            $(module).addClass('hidden');
          } else {
            $(module).removeClass('hidden');
          }
        }

        // ADD CURRENT CLASS TO TAB
        for (k=0; k < tabs.length; k++) {
          if (tabs[k] == this) {
            $(tabs[k]).addClass('current');
          } else {
            $(tabs[k]).removeClass('current');
          }
        }
      });
    }

    // LAZY LOAD IMAGES
    function lazyLoadImages(images) {
      for(l=0; images.length > l; l++){
          var image = images[l];
          if (typeof image.dataset.lazySrc != "undefined") {
            if (image.src != image.dataset.lazySrc) {
              image.src = image.dataset.lazySrc;
            }
          }
        }
    }

    function lazyLoadEvent() {
      if ("" == "1") {
        var tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-button');
        if (tabs.length > 0) {
          for(i=0; tabs.length > i; i++){
            if (i == 0) {
              var targetIdOne     = tabs[i].dataset.target,
                  tabTargetOne       = document.getElementById(targetIdOne),
                  tabTargetOneImages = tabTargetOne.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetOneImages);
            }

            tabs[i].addEventListener('click', function() {
              var tabTargetId     = this.dataset.target,
                  tabTarget       = document.getElementById(tabTargetId),
                  tabTargetImages = tabTarget.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetImages);
            });
          }
        }
      }
    }

    compileTabTargets(tabs, tabTargets);
    tabClick(tabs, tabTargets);
    lazyLoadEvent();
    
  });
           </script>

            <script src="https://content.markitcdn.com/www.chartworks.io/content/chartworks/dist/1.4.8/js/chartworks.min.js" type="text/javascript">
            </script>
            <script>
             $('.index-name').bind('click', function() {
        var index       = $(this),
            indexRic    = index.attr('data-ric'),
            indices     = $('.index-data-container').find('.index-name'),
            indexTab    = index.find('.index-tab');

        for (i=0;indices.length > i;i++) {
            $(indices[i]).removeClass('active');
            $('.index-tab').removeClass('active');
        }
        index.addClass('active');
        indexTab.addClass('active');
        renderChart(window.chartworks_token, indexRic)
    });

    const first_ric = $('.index-name')[0].dataset.ric;

    function getChartData(obj) {
        window.chartworks_token = obj.access_token;
        renderChart(obj.access_token, first_ric);
    }

    
    function renderChart(token, ric) {

        // Set the chart inputs
        var chartInputs = {
          "symbol": ric,
          "realTime": false,
          "cultureCode": "en-US",
          "fontColor": "#999999",
          "fontSize": 18,
          "upperPanelHeight": 144,
          "lowerPanelHeight": 0,
          "numDays": 1,
          "priceLineColor": "#ff8000",
          "priceLineWidth": 3,
          "showVolume": false,
          "volumeColor": "#ff8000",
          "width": 556,
          "xGridLineColor": "#ffffff",
          "xGridLineWidth": 1,
          "yGridLineColor": "#dddddd",
          "yGridLineWidth": 1
        };

        // Stringify & Encode Inputs
        var encoded = encodeURIComponent(JSON.stringify(chartInputs, null));

        // Create API call
        var url = "https://api.markitondemand.com/apiman-gateway/MOD/chartworks-image/1/Chart/price?inputs=" + encoded + "&access_token=" + token;

        // Append to our target
        $(".index-data-container .index-chart img").remove();
        $('<img />').attr("src", url).appendTo(".index-data-container .index-chart");


    }
            </script>
            <script src="https://apiservice.reuters.com/api/service/modtoken?method=get&amp;format=json&amp;callback=getChartData&amp;apikey=72461C50B1CEAD3135BA6BDA53B203D3&amp;deviceid=E7CDD293-9C3A-5AB9-9181-58E1B572DD44" type="text/javascript">
            </script>

    <div class="group wrap" id="rcs-sectionHeader">
     <header class="module-header">
      <h1 class="module-heading module-heading-page">
       Markets &amp; Finance News
      </h1>
     </header>
     <div class="ad-sponsor-page">
      <div id="div_gpt_sponsorlogo">
       <div class="ad" id="sponsorlogo">
        <script type="text/javascript">
         var dz_final = TR3.extractDartZone();
// leaderboard
if( 'sponsorlogo' == 'leaderboard'){
    //US/UK HOME FASTLANE
    if((TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("us.reuters") > -1) || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("uk.reuters") > -1) || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("jp.reuters") > -1) || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("lta.reuters") > -1)){
        if(typeof(Reuters)!='undefined' && typeof(Reuters.info)!='undefined' && typeof(Reuters.info.channel)!='undefined')
        {displayAd_sync_fastlane(dz_final,  "storychannel=" + Reuters.info.channel + ";" + adParams2 + "" );}
        else{ displayAd_sync_fastlane( dz_final, "" + adParams2 + "" ); }
    }
    else{ 
		if(typeof(Reuters)!='undefined' && typeof(Reuters.info)!='undefined' && typeof(Reuters.info.channel)!='undefined')
        { displayAd_sync(dz_final,  "storychannel=" + Reuters.info.channel + ";" + adParams2 + "");}
        else{ displayAd_sync( dz_final, "" + adParams2 + "" ); }
    }
}
else if('sponsorlogo' == 'mpu'){ googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('div_gpt_mpu'); }); }
else if('sponsorlogo' == 'mpu2'){ googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('div_gpt_mpu2'); }); }
else if('sponsorlogo' == 'mpulow'){ googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('div_gpt_mpulow'); }); }
else if('sponsorlogo' == 'leaderboardcenter'){
    if((TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("us.reuters") > -1) || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("uk.reuters") > -1) || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("jp.reuters") > -1)  || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("lta.reuters") > -1)){ googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('div_gpt_lb_center'); }); }
    else{ displayAd("div_gpt_sponsorlogo", dz_final,  [250,36], "type=sponsorlogo;" + adParams2 + "" ); }
}
else if('sponsorlogo' == 'leaderboardlow'){
        if((TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("us.reuters") > -1) || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("uk.reuters") > -1) || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("jp.reuters") > -1) || (TR3.extractDartZone().indexOf("lta.reuters") > -1)){ googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('div_gpt_lb_low'); }); }
        else{ displayAd("div_gpt_sponsorlogo", dz_final,  [250,36], "type=sponsorlogo;" + adParams2 + "" ); }
}
else{
    if(typeof(Reuters)!='undefined' && typeof(Reuters.info)!='undefined' && typeof(Reuters.info.channel)!='undefined'){
        displayAd("div_gpt_sponsorlogo", dz_final,  [250,36], "type=sponsorlogo;storychannel=" + Reuters.info.channel+ ";" + adParams2 + "" );
    } else{ displayAd("div_gpt_sponsorlogo", dz_final,  [250,36], "type=sponsorlogo;" + adParams2 + "" ); }	
}
        </script>

         Regional Markets

          News

       <section class="module-content">
        <!-- TABS -->
        <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tab-table" id="regionMarketsTabs" width="100%">
         <tbody>
          <tr>
           <th class="tab-1 tab-button current" data-target="tab-markets-us" width="33.333333333333336%">
            United States
           </th>
           <th class="tab-2 tab-button" data-target="tab-markets-emea" width="33.333333333333336%">
            Europe &amp; Middle East
           </th>
           <th class="tab-3 tab-button" data-target="tab-markets-asia" width="33.333333333333336%">
            Asia Pacific
           </th>
          </tr>
         </tbody>
        </table>
        <style>
         .tab-markets-regional .tabs {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li span,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li span.hrefClone{
    background: none !important;
    border: none !important;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current{
    background: #f5f5f5 !important;
    padding-bottom: 0px !important;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current span{
    padding-bottom: 13px;
}
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current span,
.tab-markets-regional .tabs ul li.current span.hrefClone{
    font-family: knowledge-medium,helvetica,arial,sans-serif;
}
#tab-markets-us .news-headline-list,
#tab-markets-emea .news-headline-list,
#tab-markets-asia .news-headline-list{
    margin-bottom: 40px;
}
        </style>
       </section>
      </section>
      <script>
       $(function(){

    var tabs       = $('#regionMarketsTabs .tab-button');
    var tabTargets = []

    function compileTabTargets(tabs, targetsArray) {
      for (i=0; i < tabs.length; i++) {
        var tabTargetId = $(tabs[i]).data('target');
        var tabTarget   = $('#'+tabTargetId);
        targetsArray.push(tabTarget);
      }
    }

    function tabClick(tabs, targets) {
      tabs.on('click', function() {
        var targetId = $(this).data('target');
        var target   = $('#'+targetId);

        // SHOW / HIDE MODULES
        for (j=0; j < targets.length; j++) {
          var module = targets[j][0];

          if (targetId != module.id) {
            $(module).addClass('hidden');
          } else {
            $(module).removeClass('hidden');
          }
        }

        // ADD CURRENT CLASS TO TAB
        for (k=0; k < tabs.length; k++) {
          if (tabs[k] == this) {
            $(tabs[k]).addClass('current');
          } else {
            $(tabs[k]).removeClass('current');
          }
        }
      });
    }

    // LAZY LOAD IMAGES
    function lazyLoadImages(images) {
      for(l=0; images.length > l; l++){
          var image = images[l];
          if (typeof image.dataset.lazySrc != "undefined") {
            if (image.src != image.dataset.lazySrc) {
              image.src = image.dataset.lazySrc;
            }
          }
        }
    }

    function lazyLoadEvent() {
      if ("" == "1") {
        var tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-button');
        if (tabs.length > 0) {
          for(i=0; tabs.length > i; i++){
            if (i == 0) {
              var targetIdOne     = tabs[i].dataset.target,
                  tabTargetOne       = document.getElementById(targetIdOne),
                  tabTargetOneImages = tabTargetOne.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetOneImages);
            }

            tabs[i].addEventListener('click', function() {
              var tabTargetId     = this.dataset.target,
                  tabTarget       = document.getElementById(tabTargetId),
                  tabTargetImages = tabTarget.getElementsByTagName('img');
              lazyLoadImages(tabTargetImages);
            });
          }
        }
      }
    }

    compileTabTargets(tabs, tabTargets);
    tabClick(tabs, tabTargets);
    lazyLoadEvent();
    
  });
      </script>
